snippet.title: Synth Riders | Oculus Quest and Full Release | Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Enjoy a freestyle-dance #VR rhythm alternative! Play Synth Riders on Oculus Quest & Rift, Steam VR & PSVR: http://bit.ly/playsr

Join the Synth Riders Discord Community: http://discord.synthridersvr.com/
Official website: https://synthridersvr.com/

Follow #SynthRiders:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/synthridersvr
Facebook: http://fb.me/synthridersvr
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/synthridersvr/

Trailer song: “You Know That You Love Me” by Prizm (FiXT Records)
https://www.fixtonline.com/
